Facebook Claimant Ceglia Hires New Lawyer in Suit Over Zuckerberg Contract

-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 
2011-10-21T20:13:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/facebook-claimant-ceglia-hires-new-lawyer-in-suit-over-zuckerberg-contract.html
Paul  Ceglia, the New York man who
claims a 2003 contract entitles him to half the holdings of
Facebook Inc. founder   Mark Zuckerberg , hired a new lawyer, his
fourth lead counsel since filing the lawsuit in 2010.  To contact the reporter on this story:
